title: Can't see my club
body:
Having an issue people seem to be having occasionally, can't see my club(s) in game when I enable show tags. Let me know if I can get some help c:
IGN: Yuemi

replies.body:
No worries, sometimes your account can somehow lose its link with your club. You're still there, it just won't show up for some reason. 

Hit me back up with the name of your club, and I can get my poro bros to fix it up asap!
